NPC ID7002

Mark is an adventurer located in Port Piscarilius. He is the husband of Cheryl, and was brought to Great Kourend by Captain Janaway's ship.

Speaking to him will result in him stating Cheryl where is our crate? We can't leave without our luggage!, and the chatbox giving the message He looks busy.
